title: Stade d'Honneur (Meknes)
text: Stade d'Honneur is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Meknes">Meknes</a>, <a href="Morocco">Morocco</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and hosts the home games of <a href="CODM%20Mekn%C3%A8s">CODM Meknès</a>. The stadium holds 25,000 people.
